OL,7,FAt the time, he was in the sole care
OL,8,Fof his mother's partner Christopher
OL,9,FStockton, 38, and he is is on trial at
OL,10,FTeesside Crown Court for murder and
OL,11,Fneglect, which he denies.
OL,13,FCharlie's mother, Paula Roberts, 41,
OL,14,Fwas also on trial for neglect, having
OL,15,Fdenied the charge, but entered a
OL,16,Fguilty plea on Tuesday (3 December).
