OL,4,Calleged shaking death of toddler
OL,5,CCharlie Roberts
OL,7,FShe admitted failing to seek medical
OL,8,Fhelp for her little boy in December
OL,9,F2023 and January 2024 after he
OL,10,Fsuffered injuries to his private parts
OL,11,Fand to his ear.
OL,13,FJurors were told that Charlie suffered
OL,14,Fbruising in the months before his
OL,15,Fdeath.
OL,17,FThey were told Roberts installed a spy
OL,18,Fcamera above his cot and told her
OL,19,Fbrother in August that she hid it in a
OL,20,Fplant pot as she was concerned about
OL,21,FStockton.
