OL,5,CCharlie Roberts
OL,7,FShe was out having an eye test when
OL,8,FCharlie suffered fatal injuries on 12
OL,9,FJanuary.
OL,11,FThe prosecution said Stockton, who had
OL,12,Fstayed up late playing video games,
OL,13,Fcaused those injuries, which cause
OL,14,Fwidespread brain bleeding.
OL,16,FHe made a 999 call in which he
OL,17,Frepeatedly said "come on mate" and
OL,18,F"wakey wakey" to the little boy, who
OL,19,Fwas not breathing.
